{"type": "article", "id": 7583, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-03-20T08:02:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8000, "name": "藤条椅子"}, {"id": 6892, "name": "跑车"}, {"id": 8001, "name": "3D打印椅子"}, {"id": 2284, "name": "桌子"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607151408F0awtzJQN16Mp8lr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\t Réaction Poétique Collection by Jaime Hayón\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t今年是建筑大师，现代主义建筑设计鼻祖 Le Corbusier 逝世 50 周年，西班牙设计师 Jaime Hayón 为了向他致敬，推出了一系列木制桌子。这些桌子的外形全部脱胎于 Le Corbusier 的经典设计作品，其中包括朗香教堂，这是 Le Corbusier 在 1955 年完成的作品，被誉为 20 世纪最为震撼和最具有表现力的建筑，直接影响了现代建筑的发展。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151353ItljJ3brkdXvZQyA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5491453\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151354nx9efWF0SQz1C6Mg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6025641\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151354yjiVE4pYhGQZHF2e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151354X1dlGxaBvTip8Prj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tNet Collection by Studiohiji \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t来自设计工作室 Studiohiji 的印尼籍设计师 Abie Abdillah 一直对于藤条家具有着热爱和研究，这次他在新加坡推出了一系列藤条桌椅。这些桌椅由手工编织完成，看似柔软的藤条经过编织可以形成稳固的椅子。设计师试图通过这一组作品唤起人们对于藤条材料的关注和喜爱。这款椅子有多种颜色可选，和浅色的藤条呼应，看起来活泼又简洁。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151355sTmhD8k7FIrta1RW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071513551NVDRdOUBSsfTP56.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071513569m1gGCVdAcDeTWoH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060715135657ipMr3SWnqJYaZ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151357E360WOPaNQmKSIGy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071513572drpl8WJu4oE5PH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tDurotaxis Chair by Synthesis Design + Architecture \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t洛杉矶设计建筑工作室 Synthesis Design + Architecture 受 Stratasys 公司委托，设计了这一款 3D 打印椅子，采用的是最先进的梯度 3D 打印技术。Stratasys 要求工作者设计的椅子离开了 3D 技术便无法完成，而工作室最终完成的这件作品达到的更高标准是：离开了 Stratasys 的 Objet 500 Connex3 技术便无法完成。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151358CmBERyX1lVNatKnb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66603774\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151358mEyxHozNlKFJSG7e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66603774\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151359al45DbqnPs7uTVmS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66603774\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151359xSaVO2P0YTdILXmE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66603774\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151359085TE4urcW7IfmBy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64528302\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tOru Series Furniture by Aljoud Lootah \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t这是阿联酋女设计师 Aljoud Lootah 为 2015 年迪拜设计日推出的一组作品，这个名为 Oru 的系列作品灵感来源自日本的折纸艺术，而 “Oru” 也正是日语里面“折叠”的意思。这一组作品包括一个台灯，一个椅子，一个装饰镜和一个橱柜。Aljoud Lootah 试图通过这组作品表达“简单的纸张可以折叠出无限的世界”这一理念。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071514005tu7a10MRENwrPH4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151400h6z80NJCdZDEgHUw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151401Fn8zhg4DqdXylvcu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151401PhBDHRZ3Sno8gEJq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151402onSVe7bzd3tEhFWk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151402pgfFRTE5iJbYkBcX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151403N6A3pmGYK2t7rByc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tBishop by Bandit9\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t这是一款由北京本土的机车改装厂牌 bandit9 公司打造的一款新型限量款跑车，这款跑车由 Honda Supersport 车身作为基本的架构，采用一体式的高钢级车身，配置了 90cc-125cc 引擎，车身可配搭胡桃木、橡木、柚木等材料，配以石英面层的 LED 灯，烟灰色的麂皮座椅，整部车看起来干练简洁但充满细节。这款车将限量 9 辆。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151403sFq05r78yCiXgbfW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63447433\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151404tLW3IdpkgFVz57hu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151404tDmzvlEXTU5LqBwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59168704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151405qpr2JiUKRujEOoL1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65525672\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151405zlRn1y8cbSYtqXei.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74449878\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151406JokBaS4rnGYlcU7Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69804401\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151406fGLoQR8CBW9T3xmi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74572127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151406borCaMP8UTG75qSX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607151407lrRJPpHGQdowBZOu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67359413\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}